Find each run’s best result for each combination of “n”, “m”, and “p”

The initial values are chosen not so close to the true value:

ggplot(res, aes(x = as.factor(n), y = cor)) +
  geom_boxplot() +
  facet_grid(alpha ~ beta)

best_res <- res %>% 
  group_by(n, m, p, run) %>% 
  arrange(desc(cor)) %>% 
  filter(row_number() == 1) %>% 
  ungroup()
